haversine_distance <- function(lat1, lon1, lat2, lon2) {
  R <- 3959 # Earth's radius in miles
  dLat <- (lat2 - lat1) * pi / 180
  dLon <- (lon2 - lon1) * pi / 180
  lat1 <- lat1 * pi / 180
  lat2 <- lat2 * pi / 180
  a <- sin(dLat/2)^2 + sin(dLon/2)^2 * cos(lat1) * cos(lat2)
  c <- 2 * atan2(sqrt(a), sqrt(1-a))
  d <- R * c
  return(d)
}
